8ca62f5a9a8607ade6d31c502bbe6b08cbc","tid":2222161,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"古有炸秦檜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今有習肉醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3ba87904e94d1c47cda46c721b1df363cf3371","tid":2222161,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3444e8bd099231ba85b88b144e96fd1cc023c6e2","tid":2222161,"uid":133680,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/GpbQh7RN/YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FGpbQh7RN%2FYOU.jpg&h=eacd9956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著他笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"401382cf786ff515b82fd635f6523730a0e331b4","tid":2222161,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebc6d0053a541aed1169abed9638e19dc8bf0aa9","tid":2222161,"uid":186529,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjvHJSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjvHJSi.jpg&h=3bb12fa6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec475306bf9c1fddbb358ae6eb7b0e852479fbc","tid":2222161,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNgLGHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNgLGHf.jpg&h=422cb3bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4485aba351f2bcaf38b659541dd9ce446ce7ec1","tid":2222161,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"193cbe0397